Package: whittakerr
Type: Package
Title: Whittaker Biome Classification and Mapping
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Kim",
           family = "Bridges",
           email = "kim.bridges@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for classifying locations into Whittaker biomes
    using annual mean temperature and annual precipitation. Supports
    point-based classification, Whittaker-diagram plotting, geographic
    biome mapping at multiple resolutions, vector smoothing of biome
    boundaries, and KML export for Google Earth visualization.
    Climate data are retrieved from WorldClim via the 'geodata'
    package; future-scenario projections via CMIP6 are supported
    under the same function signature.
